cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.MM 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with object detection and tracking. Additionally, it may also belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories as it involves algorithmic organization and performance optimization. The robotics (cs.RO) sub-category is also a possibility as object detection and tracking are important components of robotics. Finally, the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category may also be relevant as event recognition involves analyzing multimedia data.
